### Fraud Rule Engine - Sample API Requests

### 1. Process a Normal Transaction (Should be APPROVED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-123",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "PURCHASE",
  "category": "Groceries",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T14:30:00",
  "merchantId": "MERCH-001",
  "merchantName": "SuperMart",
  "location": "New York, NY"
}

### 2. Process a High Amount Transaction (Should trigger HIGH_AMOUNT rule)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-002",
  "customerId": "CUST-456",
  "amount": 15000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "PURCHASE",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T15:00:00",
  "merchantId": "MERCH-002",
  "merchantName": "Tech Store",
  "location": "San Francisco, CA"
}

### 3. Process a Suspicious Round Amount (Should trigger SUSPICIOUS_AMOUNT rule)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-003",
  "customerId": "CUST-789",
  "amount": 6000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "WITHDRAWAL",
  "category": "ATM",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T16:00:00",
  "merchantId": "MERCH-003",
  "merchantName": "ATM Network",
  "location": "Chicago, IL"
}

### 4. Process a Night Time Transaction (Should trigger NIGHT_TIME_TRANSACTION rule)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-004",
  "customerId": "CUST-111",
  "amount": 3500.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "PURCHASE",
  "category": "Jewelry",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T02:30:00",
  "merchantId": "MERCH-004",
  "merchantName": "Luxury Jewelers",
  "location": "Miami, FL"
}

### 5. Process Multiple Transactions for Velocity Check (Run 6 times quickly)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-VEL-001",
  "customerId": "CUST-VELOCITY",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "PURCHASE",
  "category": "Online",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-13T17:00:00",
  "merchantId": "MERCH-005",
  "merchantName": "Online Store",
  "location": "Online"
}

### 6. Get All Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions

### 7. Get Transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/1

### 8. Get Transaction by Transaction ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/transaction/TXN-001

### 9. Get Transactions by Customer ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/customer/CUST-123

### 10. Get All Fraudulent Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/fraudulent

### 11. Get All Fraud Alerts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fraud-alerts

### 12. Get Fraud Alerts by Transaction ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fraud-alerts/transaction/2

### 13. Get Fraud Alerts by Severity
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fraud-alerts/severity/HIGH

### 14. Get High Priority Alerts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fraud-alerts/high-priority

### 15. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### 16. Application Metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics
